/-
CLASS-F FILE — the `floor_kcombo` dispatch body is machine-emitted by
experiments/bb_lab/scripts/gen_assembly_2d.py (fragments pasted in by hand);
the surrounding shell and the capstone theorems are hand-maintained.
Regenerate fragments rather than hand-editing dispatch rows.
